<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>My Wellness Community</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-MCw98/SFnGE8fJT3GXwEOngsV7Zt27NXFoaoApmYm81iuXoPkFOJwJ8ERdknLPMO" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <section class="hero is-primary is-bold">
    <div class="hero-body">
        <div class="container">
        <h1 class="title">Welcome to My Wellness Community</h1>
        <h2 class="subtitle">A place for people focused on living a healthy lifestyle.</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<br>

<div class="columns">
  <div class="column">
        <section class="content">
        <div>
        <br>
        <p>
        <strong>My Wellness Community</strong> is a place for people who are focused on living a healthy lifestyle. We can connect with one another and share recipes and post some of our ideas. 
        </p>
        <p>
        My Wellness Community App is a Rails web application created by Daniel Carvalho as a portfolio project in association with Flatiron School's Online Software Engineering Program.
        </p>
        </div>
        </section>

        <% if @posts && !@posts.empty? %>
            <h3>Here's a list of all your posts:</h3>
            <% @posts.each do |post| %>
              <%= link_to post.title, post_path(post) %>
            <% end %> 
        <% end %>

        <% if @recipes && @recipes.empty? %>
            <h3>Here's a list of all your recipes:</h3>
            <% @recipes.each do |r| %>
              <%= link_to r.name, recipe_path(r) %>
            <% end %> 
        <% end %>

  </div>
</div>